      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d034n1-ptr" id="PJA04d034n1">1</a>
      
   <p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s membership on a congressional committee to consider the fortifications of one or more American ports caused him several times to exhort those in Massachusetts to greater efforts and to propose plans for the effective fortification of Boston Harbor (<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s Service in the Congress, <span>9 Feb.  27 Aug.</span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-04-02-0001-0010" class="document">No. IX</a>, above).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d034n2-ptr" id="PJA04d034n2">2</a>
      
   <p>The Declaration on Armed Vessels; see <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to James Warren, 21 March, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-04-02-0022&amp;expandNote=PJA04d033n2#PJA04d033n2" class="document">note 2</a> (above).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d034n3-ptr" id="PJA04d034n3">3</a>
      
   <p>Perhaps <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s comment here is an indication that he was working on what came to be called Thoughts on Government (<a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-04-02-0026" class="document">ante 27 MarchApril</a>, below).</p>

